Package org.frc2851.crevolib.subsystem

Class Subsystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.frc2851.crevolib.subsystem.Subsystem
  • public abstract class Subsystem
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class that defines subsystem behavior. An example of the subsystem may be a drivetrain or a shooter. A subsystem subclass should contain all code that manipulates physical subsystems.
